rows.name: Page
rows.templateHtml:
<%@ page language="java" contentType="text/html; charset=UTF-8" pageEncoding="UTF-8"%>
<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/loose.dtd">
<%@ taglib prefix="shiro" uri="http://shiro.apache.org/tags" %>
<html>
<head>
    <title>${name!'自定义表单生成'}</title>
</head>
<body>
<container>

	<!--外部js文件引用 -->
	<#if extraJsFile?? && extraJsFile != ''>
		${extraJsFile}
	</#if>
	<script src="/Lims/commonpage/js/util.js"></script>
	<script src="/Lims/commonpage/js/array.js"></script>
	<!--当前登录人信息 -->
			<input type="hidden" id="currentLoginUserId" name="currentLoginUserId" value="${r'${currentLoginUserId }'}" />
			<input type="hidden" id="currentLoginUserName" name="currentLoginUserName" value="${r'${currentLoginUserName }'}" />
			<input type="hidden" id="currentLoginUserOrgId" name="currentLoginUserOrgId" value="${r'${currentLoginUserOrgId }'}" />

	<#if processPageType??  >
		<#if processPageType=='2' || processPageType=='3'>
			<script src="/Lims/js/customform/workflow.js"></script>
			
			<!-- 工作流程创建，提交，签收，回退需要参数 -->
			<input type="hidden" id="wf_workItemState" name="state" value="${r'${workItemState }'}" />
			<input type="hidden" id="wf_fowardMode" name="fowardMode" value="${r'${fowardMode }'}" />
			<input type="hidden" id="wf_workItemId" name="workItemId" value="${r'${workItemId }'}" />
			<input type="hidden" id="wf_instanceId" name="workItemId" value="${r'${instanceId }'}" />
			<input type="hidden" id="wf_activityName" name="activityName" value="${r'${activityName }'}" />
			<input type="hidden" id="wf_userIdList" name="userIdList" />
			<input type="hidden" id="wf_nextActivityName" name="nextActivityName" />
			
		</#if>
		<#if processPageType=='2' >
			<!--代办列表页的信息 -->
			<input type="hidden" id="historyPageId" name="historyPageId" value="${r'${pageId }'}" />
			<input type="hidden" id="historyPageActivityId" name="historyPageActivityId" value="${r'${activityId }'}" />
			<input type="hidden" id="historyPageProcessId" name="historyPageProcessId" value="${r'${processId }'}" />
		</#if>
		<#if processPageType=='3'>
			<!--详情页的信息 -->
			<input type="hidden" id="detailPageHistoryPageId" name="historyPageId" value="${r'${historyPageId }'}" />
			<input type="hidden" id="detailPageHistoryPageActivityId" name="historyPageActivityId" value="${r'${historyPageActivityId }'}" />
			<input type="hidden" id="detailPageHistoryPageProcessId" name="historyPageProcessId" value="${r'${historyPageProcessId }'}" />
			<input type="hidden" id="detailPageId" name="detailPageId" value="${r'${detailPageId }'}" />
		</#if>
	</#if>

<#if isSampleInfo?? &&isSampleInfo=='1' >
		<script src="/Lims/js/pt/ptSampleInput.js"></script>
	</#if>
	<#if hasAttachmentInfo?? &&hasAttachmentInfo=='1' >
		<script src="/Lims/js/customform/attachment.js"></script>
	</#if>
	<input type="hidden" id="mainFormId" name="mainFormId" value=${r'"${mainFormId}"'} />
    <input type="hidden" id="mainFormDataId" name="mainFormDataId" value=${r'"${mainFormDataId}"'} />
	<#if global.controlCss?? && global.controlCss != ''>
	<style>
		${global.controlCss}
	</style>
	</#if>
    <#list htmls as html>
            ${html}
    </#list>
    <script type="text/javascript">
           ${script}
    </script>
	
	${globalJsFunction!''}
</container>
</body>
</html>

function editAccept(workItemId,acceptCode,acceptId) {
	judgeWFSumit(workItemId,$('#activityId').val(),function(){
		var url=getRootPath()+ $('#formName').val()
		+ '&processId=' + $('#processId').val() + '&workItemId='
		+ workItemId + '&activityId=' + $('#activityId').val()+'&pageId='+$('#detailPageId').val()+'&viewFlag='+$('#viewFlag').val();
		if(acceptId){
			url=url+'&id='+acceptId;
		}
		
		nsFrame.loadPage(url);
	});
}
function editAcceptABC(workItemId,acceptCode,acceptId) {
	judgeWFSumit(workItemId,$('#activityId').val(),function(){
		var url=getRootPath()+ $('#formNameURL').val()
		+ '&processId=' + $('#processId').val() + '&workItemId='
		+ workItemId + '&activityId=' + $('#activityId').val()+'&pageId='+$('#detailPageId').val()+'&viewFlag='+$('#viewFlag').val();
		if(acceptId){
			url=url+'&id='+acceptId;
		}
		
		nsFrame.loadPage(url);
	});
}

function editAcceptABCD(workItemId,acceptCode,acceptId,modificationType) { 
console.info('点击受理编号');
console.info(modificationType);
	judgeWFSumit(workItemId,$('#activityId').val(),function(){
		var _url=getRootPath()+ '/acceptForm/acceptInfoMain?sampleNumberingId=5&pageCode=nbwt&pageId=29430&view=1'
		+'&modificationType='+modificationType+ '&processId=' + $('#processId').val() + '&workItemId='
		+ workItemId + '&activityId=' + $('#activityId').val()+'&pageId='+$('#detailPageId').val()+'&viewFlag='+$('#viewFlag').val();
		if(acceptId){
			_url=_url+'&id='+acceptId;
		}
		
		nsFrame.loadPage(_url);
	});
}

function tableColumnItemClick(linkPath,linkParams){
            console.info("linkPath:"+linkPath+"     linkParams:"+linkParams)
            var url = null;
            if(linkParams){
                if(linkPath.indexOf('?')==-1){
                    url = getRootPath()+linkPath+	'?'+linkParams;
                }else{
                    url = getRootPath()+linkPath+'&'+linkParams;
                }
            }else{
                url = getRootPath()+linkPath;
            }
           url = url+"&historyPageId="+$('#historyPageId').val()+"&historyPageActivityId="+$('#historyPageActivityId').val()+"&historyPageProcessId="+$('#historyPageProcessId').val()+"&detailPageId="+$('#detailPageId').val();
            console.info(url);
            nsFrame.loadPage(url);
        }


function getDataInfos(){
	<#if formParams?? && formParams!='' >
		var formParams = ${formParams};
		var params = {pageId:${flagComponentInfoId},params:JSON.stringify(formParams)};
	<#else>
		var params = {pageId:${flagComponentInfoId}};
	</#if>
   $.getJSON(getRootPath()+'/commonFunction/formDatas',params,
       function (data) {
            if(data.success){
                if(data.data&&data.data.length>0){
					for(var i = 0;i<data.data.length;i++){
						var itemInfo = data.data[i];
						if(itemInfo&&itemInfo.componentIdAttr&&itemInfo.data){
							try{
                                                                var  beforeFillValue = _pageObj.beforeFillValue;
								if(typeof(beforeFillValue) == 'function'){
									itemInfo.data = beforeFillValue(itemInfo.data,itemInfo.componentIdAttr);
								}
							}catch(e){}	
							formPlane.fillValues(itemInfo.data,itemInfo.componentIdAttr);
						}
					}
				}
			}
   });
}

getDataInfos();

nsFrame.loaded();

baseDataTable.getSingleRowSelectedDataAsArr = function(tableId){
	if(tableId){
		var selectedData = baseDataTable.getSingleRowSelectedData(tableId);
		if(selectedData){
			var selectedDataArr = new Array();
			selectedDataArr[0] = selectedData;
			return selectedDataArr;
		}
	}
	return false;
}
function linkHandler(id,workItemId) {
if(workItemId){
var _url = getRootPath()+'/netStarRights/checkVoucher-main?id='+id+'&activityId='+$("#activityId").val()+'&processId='+	$("#processId").val()+"&pageId="+$("#detailPageId").val()+"&workItemId="+workItemId;
}else{
var _url = getRootPath()+'/netStarRights/checkVoucher-main?id='+id+'&activityId='+$("#activityId").val()+'&processId='+	$("#processId").val()+"&pageId="+$("#detailPageId").val();
}			
			nsFrame.loadPage(_url);
		}

rows.name: Select
rows.templateJs:
{
		id:'${id}',
		label:'${label}',
		type:'select',
		rules:'${rules}',
		column:${column},
<#if dataType?? && dataType!='' >
			dataType:'${dataType}',
		<#else>
			dataType:'name',
		</#if>
		<#if textField?? && textField!='' >
			textField:'${textField}',
		<#else>
			textField:'name',
		</#if>
		<#if valueField?? && valueField!='' >
			valueField:'${valueField}',
		<#else>
			valueField:'id',
		</#if>
		<#if scripts?? && (scripts?size>0) >
		subdata:[
				<#list scripts as script>
					${script},
				</#list>
		],
		<#else>
			<#if dataSrc?? && dataSrc!=''>
				dataSrc:'${dataSrc}',
			</#if>
			<#if url?? && url !=''>
				url:${url!''},
				<#if data?? && data!=''>
				data:${data},
				</#if>
			<#else>
				url:getRootPath()+'/commonFunction/selectValue',
				dataSrc:'rows',
				<#if data?? && data!=''>
					data:{selectComponentId:${flagComponentInfoId},params:JSON.stringify(${data})},
				<#else>
					data:{selectComponentId:${flagComponentInfoId}},
				</#if>
			</#if>
			<#if method?? && method !=''>
				method:'${method}',
			</#if>
		</#if>
		<#if changeHandler?? && changeHandler !=''>
		changeHandler:${changeHandler},
		</#if>
		<#if subFormId?? && subFormId !='' && subSqlInfo?? && subSqlInfo!=''>
		changeHandler:function (value, text) {
                                    $.ajax({
                                        <#if subParamData?? && subParamData!=''>
                                        data:{selectComponentId:${flagComponentInfoId},params:JSON.stringify(${subParamData})}, 
										<#else>
										data:{selectComponentId:${flagComponentInfoId}},
                                        </#if>
                                        url: getRootPath() + '/commonFunction/selectSubValue.json',
                                            type: 'post',
                                            success: function (data) {
                                            if (data.success) {
                                            <#if subFormId?? && subFormId!=''>
                                                formPlane.fillValues(data.data,'${subFormId}');
                                            </#if>
                                            } else {
                                                var _errStr = data.msg
                                                nsalert('获取信息失败 ' + _errStr, 'error');
                                            }
                                        },
                                        error: function (e) {
                                            nsalert('获取信息失败，请重试', 'error');
                                        }
                                    })
                                },
		</#if>
		<#if value?? && value !=''>
		value:'${value}',
		</#if>
               
		<#if hiddenExpress?? && hiddenExpress!=''>
			hidden:${hiddenExpress},
		<#else>
			<#if hidden?? >
				hidden:${hidden},
			<#else>
				hidden:false,
			</#if>
		</#if>
	    <#if readonlyExpress?? && readonlyExpress!=''>
			readonly:${readonlyExpress},
		<#else>
			<#if readonly?? >
				readonly:${readonly},
			<#else>
				readonly:false,
			</#if>
		</#if>
	        
		
}

rows.templateJs:
<#if script?? && script != ''>${script}</#if>

function editAccept(workItemId,acceptCode,acceptId) {
	judgeWFSumit(workItemId,$('#activityId').val(),function(){
		var url=getRootPath()+ $('#formName').val()
		+ '&processId=' + $('#processId').val() + '&workItemId='
		+ workItemId + '&activityId=' + $('#activityId').val()+'&pageId='+$('#detailPageId').val()+'&viewFlag='+$('#viewFlag').val();
		if(acceptId){
			url=url+'&id='+acceptId;
		}
		
		nsFrame.loadPage(url);
	});
}

function tableColumnItemClick(linkPath,linkParams){
            console.info("linkPath:"+linkPath+"     linkParams:"+linkParams)
            var url = null;
            if(linkParams){
                if(linkPath.indexOf('?')==-1){
                    url = getRootPath()+linkPath+	'?'+linkParams;
                }else{
                    url = getRootPath()+linkPath+'&'+linkParams;
                }
            }else{
                url = getRootPath()+linkPath;
            }
           url = url+"&historyPageId="+$('#historyPageId').val()+"&historyPageActivityId="+$('#historyPageActivityId').val()+"&historyPageProcessId="+$('#historyPageProcessId').val()+"&detailPageId="+$('#detailPageId').val();
            console.info(url);
            nsFrame.loadPage(url);
        }


function getDataInfos(){
	<#if formParams?? && formParams!='' >
		var formParams = ${formParams};
		var params = {pageId:${flagComponentInfoId},params:JSON.stringify(formParams)};
	<#else>
		var params = {pageId:${flagComponentInfoId}};
	</#if>
   $.getJSON(getRootPath()+'/commonFunction/formDatas',params,
       function (data) {
            if(data.success){
                if(data.data&&data.data.length>0){
					for(var i = 0;i<data.data.length;i++){
						var itemInfo = data.data[i];
						if(itemInfo&&itemInfo.componentIdAttr&&itemInfo.data){
							formPlane.fillValues(itemInfo.data,itemInfo.componentIdAttr);
						}
					}
				}
			}
   });
}

getDataInfos();

nsFrame.loaded();

baseDataTable.getSingleRowSelectedDataAsArr = function(tableId){
	if(tableId){
		var selectedData = baseDataTable.getSingleRowSelectedData(tableId);
		if(selectedData){
			var selectedDataArr = new Array();
			selectedDataArr[0] = selectedData;
			return selectedDataArr;
		}
	}
	return false;
}

if(workItemId){
var _url = getRootPath()+'/netStarRights/checkVoucher-main?id='+id+'&activityId='+$("#activityId").val()+'&processId='+	$("#processId").val()+"&pageId="+$("#detailPageId").val()+"&workItemId="+workItemId;
}else{
var _url = getRootPath()+'/netStarRights/checkVoucher-main?id='+id+'&activityId='+$("#activityId").val()+'&processId='+	$("#processId").val()+"&pageId="+$("#detailPageId").val();
}			
			nsFrame.loadPage(_url);
		}
